    &lt;/span&gt;        
    
&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Birds, Animals and Human all breath  &lt;br&gt;
and exists as long as they breath &lt;br&gt;
But only humans are aware of his own existence. &lt;br&gt;
Other exists but with with limited awareness,  &lt;br&gt;
which is good enough for survival.&lt;/p&gt;
