So asking the next question is natural for humans. &lt;br&gt;
That question is &amp;ldquo;Who Am I&amp;rdquo; &lt;br&gt;
Because of limited self awareness it is not possible  &lt;br&gt;
for birds and animals to ask this question.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
